Title: Black Market
Plot: Pegasus' new commander Fisk is murdered by black marketeers, and Lee is charged with solving the crime. Roslin seeks to stamp out the black market by introducing new trade regulations.
GuestStars: Gustavo Febres, Brad Mann, James Ashcroft, Amy Lalonde, Bill Duke, Claudette Mink, Graham Beckel, John Mann, Hayley Guiel
